import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import { Provider } from 'react-redux'
import App from './App'
import { store } from "./store"
import { Router } from 'react-router-dom'

ReactDOM.render(

  <Provider store={store}>
    <App />
  </Provider>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
